message.content: cs.SY, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.BIO, cs.ET - The paper deals with the analysis of gene regulatory networks using formal verification-like methods, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The use of linear temporal logics and symbolic bounded model checking suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-category of logic in computer science (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on evolutionary biology and the use of a weighted GRN model suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of bioinformatics (cs.BIO) and emerging technologies (cs.ET).
